text: Adu Gyamfi Senior High School is a coeducational second-cycle institution at Jamasi in the Sekyere East District of the Ashanti Region of Ghana. ==See also== * Education in Ghana * List of schools in Ghana ==References== Category:Educational institutions with year of establishment missing Category:Ashanti Region Category:High schools in Ghana Category:Public schools
